{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_08_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 言いそびれちゃった",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もう年末なんですね。お仕事を沢山いただけた\nおかげで、なんだかあっという間な気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s already the end of the year. I feel like the time\njust flew by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今月はかなりハードな日程だから、体調を崩さないか\n心配してたけど……みんな元気そうで良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This month’s schedule is pretty tight‚ so I was worried\nthat you all might get sick… I’m glad to see everyone’s doing well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに忙しいですけど……年明けすぐの\nお仕事が終わったらオフになってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is busy‚ but… We have time off\nafter we finish our first job of the new year‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そのタイミングで、月ストのみんなと\n日帰り旅行をすることになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We decided to go on a\nday trip with all the Moon Tempest members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.000000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "プライベートで五人一緒に出かけるのは久しぶりだから\nその旅行を楽しみにして頑張ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since the five of us went out together‚\nso I’m looking forward to the trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "日帰りで時間も限られてるから\n予定をしっかり決めることにしたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it’s a day trip and we have limited time‚\nwe decided to plan it out carefully‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "「ご飯はどこで食べよう」「お土産はどこで買おうか」\nなんて話はいくらしても足りなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t stop talking about things like “Where should we eat?”‚ “Where should we buy souvenirs?”…\nWe can’t stop talking about things like “Where should we eat?”‚ “Where should we buy souvenirs?”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとした空き時間が出来るたびに\nみんなで何度も話し合ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever we have a little free time‚\nwe all get together and discuss it again and again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "充実したオフになりそうだな。それにしても……\n月ストでも遠出か。最近の琴乃はアクティブだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like you’ll have a fulfilling break. By the way…\nMoon Tempest is going on a trip? You’ve been pretty active lately‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "最近、好きなアイドルのライブによく行ってただろ？\n忙しい中で何度も行くのは凄いなと思ってたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been going to your favorite idol’s live shows a lot lately‚ haven’t you?\nI thought it was amazing how you managed to go so many times despite being busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5507147282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "言われてみれば……確かに、最近はかなり頻繁に\n行ってましたね。遠征もしてましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it… I have been going quite frequently lately.\nI even went on a trip to see one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3317549388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "楽しかったし勉強になりました……あ\nどうしよう……今度の旅行の分、残ってるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was fun‚ and I learned a lot… Oh‚\nI wonder… Do I have enough left for the trip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666781108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ！\nなんでもないです、なんでもないですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no!\nIt’s nothing‚ it’s nothing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2333498637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年が明けて間もない頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Shortly after the New Year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4000165303,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6646323000066,
          "startTime": 100.6666811626
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4599.9979656000105,
          "startTime": 104.0000144959
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6333478292
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6333478292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いたいた。琴乃……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ there you are. Kotono… Hm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5000144959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7333478292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……やっぱりライブに行き過ぎたみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do… I think I went to too many live shows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7333478292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8000211081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "いつもはすずのこと叱ってるのに\nこれじゃ人のこと言えない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always scolding Suzu‚\nbut now I’m in no position to say anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6000211081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時って誰に相談したらいいんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who should I talk to about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4000211081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.0000205996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "お小遣いの前借りなんて恥ずかしいし\nお年玉は預けちゃったし……うーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s embarrassing to ask for an advance on my allowance‚\nand I gave my New Year’s money to Mom… Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9333539329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0666842146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、明けましておめでとう\n新年早々打ち合わせを入れてしまってすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ Happy New Year.\nSorry for scheduling a meeting so early in the new year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6666842146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3666679385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあっ！？　{user}さん……\nあ、明けましておめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek!? {user}-san…\nOh‚ Happy New Year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9000012718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきすずの名前が聞こえた気がするんだが……\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I heard Suzu’s name just now…\nWhat’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5333244327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.5333234155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、実は旅行に使うお小遣いが足りなく……\n……じゃ、じゃなくて！　えっと……あ、そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ actually‚ I’m short on allowance money for the trip…\n…N-no‚ I mean! Um… Oh‚ that’s right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2666567489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.2666394556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さっき寮で、すずが冬休みの課題に\n全く手をつけてないことが分かって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "J-just now‚ at the dorm‚ we found out that Suzu\nhasn’t done any of her winter break homework…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.299972789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "沙季には言わないでくださいましーって言ってたん\nですけど、ふと見たら扉の隙間から沙季が見ていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was saying‚ “Please don’t tell Saki-san~!”‚ but\nI happened to look up and saw Saki peeking through the door…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9333040878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
